<Class name="CM_EDIData" id="9f848ac9-374e-447a-9f5c-091341c0a650">
    <superclass name="CM_Object"/>
    <subclassPersistentAllowed/>
    <subclassSharedTransientAllowed/>
    <subclassTransientAllowed/>
    <abstract/>
    <text>A CM_EDIData class must be created for each style of data supported by EDI.
Each class must have a corresponding CM_EDIFile class. CM_EDIFile many-to-one CM_EDIData.

Each data class either has a corresponding CM_EDITrackedItem class or is a group capable
of containing several CM_EDITrackedItems (CCMS MES 1011).


See CM_EDIControllerAgent.</text>
    <DbClassMap file="edi"/>
